Dr Kempa was my favourite professor by far! Easy material as long as you are interested in it, but there was a lot of reading involved. Overall he's great!

One of the best professor. Super energetic and GREAT lectures. One of the best profs Ive had so far. His lectures are very entertaining and his passion for the subject clearly shows. Honestly, nothing bad to say about Kempa! He gives great, interactive lectures. He's truly a great prof and is understanding!

By far the best prof I had that semester. I always looked forward to his class. He's so so funny and he genuinely cares about his students. He was very accommodating of the individual needs of each student and was so receptive to feedback. Almost switched my major to crim because of his class.

Professor Kempa is one of the best professors Ive come across in all my time in university. He actually makes me want to attend 8 am classes and makes the course so enjoyable. Kempa is a really good prof who makes his lectures interesting and is super straightforward with assignments. As long as you go to the lectures before the exam/midterm, you'll be fine
Kempa is a great prof. His lectures are entertaining and he makes the content easy to understand. Would definitely recommend

Very easy class. Didn't read nor listen during the lectures. Exams are written essays. Easy to write about whatever and still get an A. Kinda feel bad for taking advantage of how chill he is but whatever.

Super fun prof. Very easy going with due dates and extensions. Incorporates current events into the course learning and allows for casual discussions. He also sang and played the guitar at the beginning of class on days that class was at 8:30 am.

Amazing prof! He was funny & kept his lectures entertaining. One paper, one midterm and a take-home exam. He grades fairly, also allowed me to resubmit a paper for a higher grade which was great. Not hard to pass. Textbook for readings but I personally didnt use mine much

Kempa is literally the best. He explains everything super clearly and always clarifies when people have questions. He makes class super fun even in the morning and online. Clearly knows his stuff, will definitely try to take another class with him.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Get ready to read', 'Hilarious']

Kempa is a great prof. The readings for this course are really heavy but he is super fun and definitely recommend for any course! He knows the material really well and is great at answering questions.

The highlight of my first semester. Super laid-back and he made class so fun. I will definitely try to take another one of his classes!
I loved this class. He makes the subject interesting and easy to understand.

Knowledgeable, knows alot about criminology.

by far the most charismatic prof you'll ever have. super entertaining, he uses accents all the time; you'll laugh. He's vocabulary is ridiculous so you might feel super lost sometimes. You feel like even though you may not enjoy criminology his teaching style makes up for it.
